::Magmatron::

    "I would like you to take Bazooka and see if you can find any 
stragellers." Magmatron said. "If you can bring them back here to my base, 
but shut down their optic sensors first."
    Bazooka went on his way. "Bobertron, take this. If you find Shredder 
press this button, I will be able to talk to him in person. He seems not to 
have answered my call. Please don't get into any fights."
